Michael Schumacher 's 16-year-old son Mick begins his Formula 4 career in Germany this weekend .
Schumers Junior is part of the Dutch Van Amersfoort Racing team in the 2015 ADAC Formula 4 series after finishing second in the world , European and German kart championships .
His debut in single-seater racing gets underway at the Motorsport Arena Oschersleben .